      "type": "weekly_digest",
      "status": "pending",
      "subject": "This week at The Quarry — Apr 28",
      "htmlBody": "<div style=\"background:#f4f5f7;padding:2rem 1rem;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;color:#1c1f26;line-height:1.6;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem 1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\">\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:2px solid #9a7b2a;\">\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:#1c1f26;letter-spacing:0.02em;\">THE QUARRY</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9a7b2a;margin:0 0 24px 0;\">This Week at The Quarry &mdash; April 28&ndash;May 4, 2026</p><p style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;line-height:1.3;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">No live music this week &mdash; but the patio is ready.</p><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">The calendar is clear this week, and with spring weather settling in, it&rsquo;s a great time to grab a table outside. Come as you are &mdash; no reservation required for the patio.</p><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 32px 0;\">Live music and events are coming up soon. Check the full calendar to see what&rsquo;s ahead and reserve early &mdash; weekends fill quickly.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 32px 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:3px;\">See What&rsquo;s Coming Up</a></div><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">See you out here,<br><span style=\"color:#9a7b2a;\">The Quarry</span></p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:2rem auto 0;padding:1.5rem 1rem;border-top:1px solid #e0e3e8;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;color:#858d9e;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <strong style=\"color:#4b5263;\">The Quarry</strong> &middot; 3960 Highway Z, New Melle, MO 63385\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">thequarrystl.com</a> &middot;\n    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">Facebook</a>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n    You're receiving this because you signed up, booked a reservation, or attended an event at The Quarry.\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/unsubscribe?email={email}\" style=\"color:#858d9e;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "innerHtml": "<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#9a7b2a;margin:0 0 24px 0;\">This Week at The Quarry &mdash; April 28&ndash;May 4, 2026</p><p style=\"font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;line-height:1.3;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">No live music this week &mdash; but the patio is ready.</p><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;\">The calendar is clear this week, and with spring weather settling in, it&rsquo;s a great time to grab a table outside. Come as you are &mdash; no reservation required for the patio.</p><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 32px 0;\">Live music and events are coming up soon. Check the full calendar to see what&rsquo;s ahead and reserve early &mdash; weekends fill quickly.</p><div style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 32px 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/events\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:3px;\">See What&rsquo;s Coming Up</a></div><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">See you out here,<br><span style=\"color:#9a7b2a;\">The Quarry</span></p></div>",
